{"tid":2403491,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾侮辱新屋嶺輪姦案受害人的 會員Frizzle(港豬), 嘗試合理化警魔呃宿舍","createTime":"2021-02-11T06:26:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T14:46:32.000Z","uid":26770,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d2019f2992196f147fb19887533afe7f5071dade","tid":2403491,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:26:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2403475/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2403475/page/1</a><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">#12 以會員名英德納雄耐爾#165028 話呃宿舍15年無損公眾利益<br />\n---------------------------------<br />\n<span class=\"red\">條友曾以會員名 何東精神（團結）做5毛</span></span><br />\n<br />\n會員 #165028 - 何東精神（團結）<br />\n，前稱純正港人(港豬)，離地中產，天安門旅遊，Frizzle(港豬)，Alexander(離地)極有可能係五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍, 請大家多加注意!<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 周街都貼連豬搞到心都煩哂</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1677596/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>睇見隻豬就火滾想撕左佢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 誠哥真係好醒目</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1628499/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>開金口講句要對年青人網開一面<br />\n而家旗下百佳, 豐澤等避開一劫<br />\n如果唔係被暴徒燒毀打爛唔知幾多間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家見到黑衫蒙面阻住我架車都唔出聲屌佢地<br />\n作狀支持佢地俾個like 等佢地放行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 想同琴晚太子站嘅一個勇武道歉</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1526091/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>因為我當時太驚又怕死<br />\n所以同其他乘客撞你出門口<br />\n希望你無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原諒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - 好怕d勇武派</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1503651/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>街上面見到佢地都會避之則吉<br />\n怕會招惹埋d警察<br />\n琴日黃大仙站成班又面罩又防具咁衝入車廂<br />\n嚇到我下個站即刻落車</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<code>#1 - （求屌醒）一直唔明白你地搞抗爭做咩</code><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320673/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<blockquote>我80後 本身都係中產階級 收入穩定又係專業人士<br />\n雖然近呢個月都聽左好多理據話要爭取好多野<br />\n包括撤回逃犯條例 調整警權過大 之類<br />\n但係我就唔明點解一定要搞到武力衝突先收手<br />\n再加上止舉令警民官民矛盾越來越大 對香港真係好咩<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞咁多野 真心唔明每個星期搞一兩單衝突暴動真係好咩 已經港九新界都搞砸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">#1 - 想報仇</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1767121\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1767121</a><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>發現女朋友個WhatsApp 有同第二個男仔有纏綿對話<br />\n我知道個男仔有參加社會又搞衝擊<br />\n宜家想搞佢罪証再報警篤灰</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ea2f2ae95809b7381b52f0260660ca094558fc8e","tid":2403491,"uid":1886,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:27:59.000Z","msg":"會員編號：#165028<br />\r會員註冊日期：2018/1/1<br />\r入 LIST 原因：曾以網名「Frizzle(港豬)」對手足幸災樂禍，近日又以其他網名對遭警暴對待的市民講風涼話。<br />\r<br />\r<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Flihkg_on9_list&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLClkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=622d4173\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list</a><br />\r<br />\r<blockquote><img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/165028/165028.1_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2F165028%2F165028.1_.png&h=6459d207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/165028/165028.2_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2F165028%2F165028.2_.png&h=5dd4eec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/165028/165028.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ%2FLIHKG_on99%2F165028%2F165028.3_.png&h=4aaffa81&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\r<br />\r<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\r<br />\r<em><span class=\"small\">上述資料更新日期：2020/8/31<br />\rP.S. 呢個唔係五毛 LIST，係戇鳩 LIST，可以畀大家認識到比較特別嘅會員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。</span></em>"},{"pid":"ce41cc9b4cd2c526288cb3f62043f5eb999d0c63","tid":2403491,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:29:26.000Z","msg":"關鍵係admin縱容班支那5毛狂改名, 點解會員名係可以改呢?<br />\n<br />\n<ins>因為大把五毛係所謂自幹五無中共科水, 自由改會員名係降低班友成本</ins>"},{"pid":"3e7e69308c5b82cf7bdfab34e32da63a5e9f4f5e","tid":2403491,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"一早block咗條毛"},{"pid":"88794532dac5211098f99cd62d0b8f6919948c0f","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:31:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8b9e7d0ca61947f2fe3483524c9c90cbf3e3d0ca","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:31:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c8a03004aaf9c44ac53049320c223aede7f34aea","tid":2403491,"uid":219128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:32:05.000Z","msg":"呢個真係知名五毛黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時見到佢留言都會追擊下佢"},{"pid":"4ab6a84167f03fd5f05555ff2f2ab27342048abb","tid":2403491,"uid":26770,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"其實外國大把討論區係唔比改名<br />\n我留意到支那五毛次次一臭左就改名,一個帳戶改6,7次大有人在<br />\n<br />\nadmin應該發信通知2月尾前可以容許改最後一次名<br />\n2月後就永久封鎖改名功能"},{"pid":"95c85fd0635b4ef4c67327cc6c7ef9044ea53cf9","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8910169cbc893a7e92726d23ae5579c0351c5c8f","tid":2403491,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vsdmukM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvsdmukM.jpg&h=8cf756b0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"718c869da19f9218a79b961372e0d5fd3e5b4790","tid":2403491,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"95c85fd0635b4ef4c67327cc6c7ef9044ea53cf9","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主 整合<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"其實我係抄<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1969335/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1969335/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n#3  Pantoloc#195<br />\n<br />\n<ins>感謝會員Pantoloc幫手</ins>"},{"pid":"f076a8684ab306a97896049941372753f9b54d64","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:34:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1c56b66ab9eb16e30f7d53cc1ce4999cee24e2ef","tid":2403491,"uid":234428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:35:13.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"62d83709715def47af8eb058ac83e007510732f0","tid":2403491,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e7e69308c5b82cf7bdfab34e32da63a5e9f4f5e","tid":2403491,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:30:40.000Z","msg":"一早block咗條毛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T06:37:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://bit.ly/lihkg_on9_list\" data-sr-url=\"h